FBIS4-15656 "drsov069_b_94015" FBIS-SOV-94-069 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Bragin of Ostankino Appointed Deputy Culture Minister Bragin of Ostankino Appointed Deputy Culture Minister LD0804175094 Moscow NTV in Russian 1500 GMT 8 Apr 94 LD0804175094 Moscow NTV Russian BFN [Text] We have learned that Russian Culture Minister Yevgeniy Sidorov has acquired a new deputy. Vyacheslav Bragin began his new duties on 6 April. Thus, the former chairman of Ostankino TV and radio company has been farmed out to culture. Maybe culture will be luckier than Ostankino.
